        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Support z.ai BigModel team usage",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n- Add z.ai BigModel team coding plan usage for saved token accounts across Settings, CLI, and config.\r\n- Send BigModel team selectors/headers for quota, model, and hourly requests; personal accounts clear team context.\r\n- Validate z.ai quota/API host endpoint overrides before credentialed team requests.\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n- Team accounts use `usageScope: team`, `organizationId`, and `workspaceID`.\r\n- z.ai team scope remains account-level only; `Z_AI_USAGE_SCOPE` is intentionally unsupported.\r\n- `CHANGELOG.md` is untouched; release-note context stays in this PR.\r\n- Existing legacy z.ai Keychain token migration is unchanged.\r\n\r\n## Live Proof\r\n- Local BigModel CN team-token probe returned API data with `1 week window`, `Monthly` (MCP), and `5 hours window`; token/org/project values were not posted.\r\n- The menu screenshot below shows the live usage windows. The redacted Settings screenshot shows account-level BigModel team configuration without posting full identifiers.\r\n\r\n## Screenshots/GIFs\r\n<img width=\"297\" height=\"513\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5020c972-90e3-44c1-93fa-128e5c7b5d22\" />\r\n<img width=\"517\" height=\"652\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a5006d77-6c4e-4b07-8a24-be94e84c6282\" />\r\n\r\n## Test Plan\r\n- `swift test --filter ZaiSettingsReaderTests`\r\n- `swift test --filter ZaiBigModelTeamScopeTests`\r\n- `swift test --filter CLIConfigCommandTests`\r\n- `swift test --filter LocalizationLanguageCatalogTests`\r\n- `swift test --filter ProviderConfigEnvironmentTests`\r\n- `swift test --filter StatusMenuTests`\r\n- `make check`\r\n- `make test`\r\n- `git diff --check`\r\n\n",
